    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46-generation M3 is a purist-spec example featuring the S54 3.2L inline-six engine, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is paired with a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential, ensuring mechanical grip and precise power delivery. Recent service includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and a reinforced rear subframe\u2014critical preventative measures for this chassis. The suspension has been refreshed with polyurethane bushings and Bilstein B6 dampers for improved lateral stability and steering feedback. While the finish shows minor road-derived patina, the mechanical synchronization and compression values remain strong, making this a tactile and responsive driver's car.",
